text: Juan René Serrano Gutiérrez (born 23 February 1984) is an archer from Mexico. René Serrano competed at the 2004 Summer Olympics, 2008 Summer Olympics, and the 2012 Summer Olympics.Juanjo SerranoJuan Rene SERRANO == References == Category:1984 births Category:Living people Category:Mexican archers Category:Olympians for Mexico
